$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_skin

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_skin -  This method sets the current skin of the living object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_skin(string word)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the new skin type
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/armour.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the current skin of the living object.  This can
be done by the race object and by specific spells or effects.
.EP

